'''"Mouse" Temple''' was a small, nervous [[Con artist/Legends|con artist]] who was [[Politics/Legends|politician]] [[Mon Mothma/Legends|Mon Mothma's]] contact on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Renor]], and was supposed to arrange her transport to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] shortly after the formation of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Mothma's entourage was captured by [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|Imperial Security Bureau]] agents, and Mothma herself was taken by [[Imperial Senate/Legends|Imperial Senator]] [[Pel Talon]]'s personal guard. "Mouse" still boarded the [[Starship/Legends|ship]] that was planned to get Mothma to the Outer Rim, the [[Blackjack (YT-1300 light freighter)|''Blackjack'']], captained by [[Jax Keyn]].

